COMBATGUARD is a new generation of 4x4 armoured combat vehicle designed and manufactured by IMI (Israel Military Industries), unveiled in 2014.
It features a monocoque central crew capsule of all-welded steel with an appliqu√© armour package, claimed to provide a high level of protection against small arms fire, mines, improvised explosive devices (IEDs) and explosive formed projectiles. It has Iron Fist (countermeasure) Bright Arrow active protection system against projectiles and missiles.
It can ford water obstacles 1.5 meter deep, travel a 35% side slopes and climb over 70% gradient, vertical obstacles up to 80 cm in forward drive and in reverse. Capable of 90 degree approach and departure angles.
In use by President of Turkmenistan.
